    <p>
      experienced across the full stack with a strong emphasis on backend
      systems, data modeling, and infrastructure.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="skills-grid">
    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>languages</h3>
      <ul class="skill-list">
        <li>javascript (es6+)</li>
        <li>typescript</li>
        <li>sql</li>
        <li>python</li>
        <li>go</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>backend & frameworks</h3>
      <ul class="skill-list">
        <li>node.js / express / fastify</li>
        <li>nestjs</li>
        <li>graphql / apollo</li>
        <li>prisma / typeorm</li>
        <li>grpc</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>databases & storage</h3>
      <ul class="skill-list">
        <li>postgresql</li>
        <li>mysql</li>
        <li>mongodb</li>
        <li>redis</li>
        <li>timescaledb</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>infrastructure & tooling</h3>
      <ul class="skill-list">
        <li>docker</li>
        <li>kubernetes</li>
        <li>aws / gcp</li>
        <li>ci/cd (github actions)</li>
        <li>prometheus / grafana</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>testing & reliability</h3>
      <ul class="skill-list">
        <li>jest / vitest</li>
        <li>supertest / integration tests</li>
        <li>cypress / playwright</li>
        <li>load testing (k6)</li>
        <li>contract testing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-category">
      <h3>tools & platforms</h3>
      <ul class="skill-list">
        <li>git / github</li>
        <li>docker / podman</li>
        <li>vercel / netlify</li>
        <li>aws / gcp</li>
        <li>terraform</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>expertise areas</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>performance & scaling</h3>
      <p>
        focused on backend performance: query tuning, caching strategies,
        connection pooling, and horizontal scaling patterns.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>data integrity & reliability</h3>
      <p>
        practices around schema migrations, ACID principles, backups, and
        transactional integrity for production systems.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>architecture & scalability</h3>
      <p>
        experienced designing maintainable service-oriented systems,
        event-driven pipelines, and robust deployment workflows.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
